Trolls get regen/bash<br>
Iksar get AC bonus<br>
Barbarians get bash/nightblind<br>
<br>
<br>
These are stupid reason in my opion there nothing i whant something that makes you whant to play that race for a certain reason like being a gnome&quot;<br>
<br>
What DO you want then? The design team (in discussing things like Mana Caps) have already stated that player attributes will not be allowed to exceed 255. As an ogre, you DO get the most envied of all the racial abilities (frontal stun immunity... look at the number of secondary/alt/twink warriors out there and most are ogres for just that reason). Adding more racial specific abilities will just add more arguments about balance, instead this time it will be racial rather than class-based and as slow as VI is in addressing other balance issues, are you sure this a road you want to go down?<br>
